snippet.title: cybeRRRevolution - Out August 29, 2024
snippet.description:
Play as Sepsis, Rebel, and Barrett in a post-war, post-disaster reality known only as cybeRRRevolution. 

Out on August 29, 2024: https://brujeriaatwerk.itch.io/cyberrrevolution

Trailer credits:
Soundtrack - The Nexus Rasp https://nexusrasp.bandcamp.com/
Audio mastering - TV-MA https://www.tvmanoise.com/
Voice over - Chris Kalhoon
